WEBVTT

00:00:18.977 --> 00:00:22.564
[footsteps]

00:00:28.737 --> 00:00:30.113
Hi, Lina...

00:00:31.823 --> 00:00:33.283
Tatsuya...

00:00:35.077 --> 00:00:37.162
I guess you heard from Ray?

00:00:37.204 --> 00:00:38.330
Yeah.

00:00:38.372 --> 00:00:40.874
I won't be teaming up with you.

00:00:40.916 --> 00:00:42.167
Yeah, I know.

00:00:42.209 --> 00:00:45.003
I mean, it makes sense.
We live in two different worlds.

00:00:45.045 --> 00:00:46.255
[gasps]

00:00:55.472 --> 00:01:00.477
♪

00:02:39.993 --> 00:02:42.454
[MIZUKI] Tatsuya, stop!
Wait a second.

00:02:42.496 --> 00:02:45.248
From what I can see, it seems
there's a parasite aura

00:02:45.290 --> 00:02:46.958
30 degrees to the right
of the direction

00:02:46.958 --> 00:02:48.669
you're currently heading in.

00:02:51.505 --> 00:02:53.256
[HONOKA]
Yeah, I see them, too!

00:02:53.298 --> 00:02:54.216
There are three of them.

00:02:54.257 --> 00:02:57.177
Looks like one woman,
and two men.

00:02:57.219 --> 00:02:59.846
[HONOKA gasps] A girl in a mask
is running toward the parasites

00:02:59.888 --> 00:03:01.598
from the opposite direction.

00:03:19.157 --> 00:03:20.367
[grunts]

00:03:29.251 --> 00:03:31.712
[LINA] I came to Japan as one
of the strongest magicians

00:03:31.753 --> 00:03:32.963
in the world.

00:03:36.508 --> 00:03:39.928
[LINA] But... the head‐to‐head
with Miyuki ended in my defeat.

00:03:50.105 --> 00:03:52.149
[LINA]
To add further insult to injury,

00:03:52.190 --> 00:03:56.153
I suffered an even more
decisive loss to Tatsuya.

00:03:56.194 --> 00:03:58.822
[PARASITE A shouts]

00:03:59.740 --> 00:04:01.491
[LINA]
Despite all that...

00:04:01.533 --> 00:04:04.119
...I'll make sure that I
carry out the role of Sirius,

00:04:04.161 --> 00:04:05.996
the commander of the Stars!

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:08.290
[gasps]

00:04:10.500 --> 00:04:11.543
[PARASITE C]
Tsk!

00:04:11.585 --> 00:04:12.919
[grunts]

00:04:15.797 --> 00:04:17.007
[ERIKA]
I've got this!

00:04:19.009 --> 00:04:20.218
[grunts]

00:04:20.260 --> 00:04:21.803
[PARASITE C gasps]

00:04:21.845 --> 00:04:23.054
[PARASITE B gasps]

00:04:27.476 --> 00:04:29.644
[PARASITE C groans]

00:04:32.230 --> 00:04:33.440
[ERIKA]
Hmph.

00:04:40.530 --> 00:04:41.615
Mikihiko!

00:04:41.656 --> 00:04:42.866
Roger!

00:04:50.415 --> 00:04:53.376
[ERIKA gasps] Let's take
a closer look, here.

00:04:53.418 --> 00:04:55.796
[ERIKA]
Oh!

00:04:55.837 --> 00:04:57.589
Alright, that's one down.

00:05:02.219 --> 00:05:03.428
[gasps]

00:05:08.266 --> 00:05:09.476
One got away.

00:05:09.518 --> 00:05:10.936
Mizuki, can you see it?

00:05:10.977 --> 00:05:12.437
No, I'm so sorry.

00:05:12.521 --> 00:05:15.649
I'm too far away to make
out individual movements.

00:05:15.690 --> 00:05:18.235
I see. Well, don't worry
about it, then.

00:05:18.276 --> 00:05:19.861
I'll figure it out.

00:05:19.903 --> 00:05:22.113
Angie Sirius!

00:05:22.155 --> 00:05:23.782
What do you want?

00:05:23.824 --> 00:05:24.699
[TATSUYA]
Could you not kill them

00:05:24.741 --> 00:05:26.993
before we finish sealing them?

00:05:27.035 --> 00:05:29.246
Cleanup's going to
be a pain as it is.

00:05:29.287 --> 00:05:30.497
[gasps]

00:05:31.790 --> 00:05:33.834
[ANGIE]
That has nothing to do with me.

00:05:33.875 --> 00:05:36.211
All I need to do is deal
with the deserters.

00:05:36.253 --> 00:05:38.213
You mean Sirius's mission?

00:05:38.255 --> 00:05:40.549
What I'm saying here is,
I want you to do that

00:05:40.590 --> 00:05:43.176
after we seal the
parasites' main bodies.

00:05:43.218 --> 00:05:45.387
One of them already escaped.

00:05:45.428 --> 00:05:48.431
Sorry, but that isn't part
of my stated mission.

00:05:48.473 --> 00:05:52.644
My duty as the Sirius is to
focus on completing that task.

00:05:56.147 --> 00:05:57.649
[ERIKA]
That was Lina, wasn't it?

00:05:57.691 --> 00:06:00.026
It's like she's a totally
different person.

00:06:00.068 --> 00:06:01.653
Why would you think it's her?

00:06:01.695 --> 00:06:03.280
Some of her mannerisms...

00:06:03.321 --> 00:06:05.657
The way she gestures,
runs, moves her head...

00:06:05.699 --> 00:06:08.034
But mostly, it's her
eyes that give it away.

00:06:08.076 --> 00:06:09.828
I'm pretty impressed.

00:06:09.870 --> 00:06:12.747
I know you already know this,
but keep it quiet.

00:06:12.789 --> 00:06:13.832
[ERIKA]
Okay.

00:06:13.874 --> 00:06:15.417
[TATSUYA]
And, incidentally,

00:06:15.458 --> 00:06:18.003
I'll tell you the same
thing I just told her.

00:06:18.044 --> 00:06:19.796
You mean, not to kill them?

00:06:19.838 --> 00:06:20.881
Exactly.

00:06:20.922 --> 00:06:22.757
As long as the host doesn't die,

00:06:22.799 --> 00:06:25.802
the parasite remains
unable to exit the body.

00:06:25.844 --> 00:06:28.013
So you have to nonlethally
disable them.

00:06:28.054 --> 00:06:29.764
[ERIKA]
Hmph. Sorry, Tatsuya.

00:06:29.806 --> 00:06:32.976
but I'm afraid I'm not going
to be able to do that.

00:06:33.018 --> 00:06:35.186
I've been prepared for
my opponent to kill me

00:06:35.228 --> 00:06:38.315
ever since I took on the sword
as the weapon of my choice.

00:06:38.356 --> 00:06:41.151
So, when I think about
how my life might end

00:06:41.192 --> 00:06:42.694
by another's hand?

00:06:42.736 --> 00:06:45.155
Well, I can't leave them
alive and deliberately

00:06:45.196 --> 00:06:46.531
extend their suffering.

00:06:46.573 --> 00:06:50.160
[sighs]
Can't argue with that.

00:06:50.201 --> 00:06:52.120
Guess I'll just have
to put in more work.

00:06:52.162 --> 00:06:53.371
[ERIKA chuckles]

00:06:55.540 --> 00:06:56.958
Hey, you guys are late!

00:06:57.000 --> 00:07:00.337
Oh, shut up! We're trying
to do the best we can!

00:07:00.378 --> 00:07:01.588
[TATSUYA gasps]

00:07:08.303 --> 00:07:10.055
[MIYUKI]
Brother...!

00:07:10.096 --> 00:07:13.808
[TATSUYA] I don't believe this.
They're the Batto‐tai.

00:07:13.850 --> 00:07:17.395
A commando infantry platoon
under JGDF's First Division

00:07:17.437 --> 00:07:19.856
and comprised solely of
magicians specializing in

00:07:19.898 --> 00:07:22.108
hand‐to‐hand combat.

00:07:22.150 --> 00:07:24.653
But why would this unit
influenced by the Kudou family

00:07:24.694 --> 00:07:26.988
be mobilized now?

00:07:27.030 --> 00:07:28.907
Panzer, activate!

00:07:30.617 --> 00:07:32.285
You and I will take these guys.

00:07:32.327 --> 00:07:35.288
Glad to. You and Miyuki
can go on ahead, Tatsuya.

00:07:35.330 --> 00:07:37.666
Alright then.
They're all yours.

00:07:37.707 --> 00:07:38.833
Come on, let's go.

00:07:38.875 --> 00:07:41.127
Right with you, Brother.

00:07:41.169 --> 00:07:42.504
[BATTO‐TAIS grunt]

00:07:44.047 --> 00:07:46.007
All right, then.

00:07:46.049 --> 00:07:47.801
Let's make short
work of these guys,

00:07:47.842 --> 00:07:49.678
then we can catch
up with the others.

00:07:49.719 --> 00:07:51.721
No problem. We'll be out
of here before they

00:07:51.763 --> 00:07:53.306
even hit the ground.

00:07:55.308 --> 00:07:58.937
[MIYUKI gasps]
Oh, no, Brother...

00:07:58.979 --> 00:08:00.313
What happened here?

00:08:09.406 --> 00:08:11.282
Lina, get back now!

00:08:11.324 --> 00:08:13.243
Just stay out of my business!

00:08:14.953 --> 00:08:16.162
[PARASITE D gasps]

00:08:22.919 --> 00:08:24.004
[TATSUYA]
Parasites...

00:08:24.045 --> 00:08:27.090
They can use magic literally
just by thinking it.

00:08:27.132 --> 00:08:30.635
Lina's greatest weapon,
is her spell activation speed.

00:08:30.677 --> 00:08:32.846
But even with that
tremendous asset,

00:08:32.887 --> 00:08:34.973
when up against six parasites,

00:08:35.015 --> 00:08:38.643
it's clear that our top priority
right now must be defense.

00:08:38.685 --> 00:08:39.602
So...

00:08:39.644 --> 00:08:40.395
[TATSUYA]
Miyuki!

00:08:40.437 --> 00:08:42.272
Right! I'm on it, Brother!

00:08:46.901 --> 00:08:48.111
[PARASITES gasp]

00:08:49.988 --> 00:08:51.531
[PARASITES yells]

00:08:51.573 --> 00:08:52.782
[PARASITES gasp]

00:09:01.624 --> 00:09:02.834
[gasps]

00:09:05.503 --> 00:09:08.089
[LEO shouts]

00:09:10.258 --> 00:09:11.468
[BATTO‐TAI E grunts]

00:09:14.554 --> 00:09:15.764
You saved me.

00:09:15.805 --> 00:09:17.223
Yeah, yeah, you're welcome.

00:09:17.265 --> 00:09:19.059
[MIKIHIKO]
Erika, Leo, be careful!

00:09:19.100 --> 00:09:22.062
[MIZUKI] The parasite's
main body is right there!

00:09:22.103 --> 00:09:23.146
[LEO]
Doton?!

00:09:23.188 --> 00:09:25.440
[shouts]

00:09:25.482 --> 00:09:26.357
[LEO]
Schild!

00:09:27.442 --> 00:09:28.860
[LEO growls]

00:09:28.902 --> 00:09:31.112
[MIKIHIKO] Leo, you realize
that's a parasite?!

00:09:31.154 --> 00:09:32.363
[groans]

00:09:34.991 --> 00:09:36.159
[ERIKA]
Oh, crap!

00:09:38.787 --> 00:09:40.080
[shouts]

00:09:40.121 --> 00:09:41.873
[ERIKA]
Pixie!

00:09:41.915 --> 00:09:44.292
[LEO shouts]

00:09:56.221 --> 00:09:58.014
[TATSUYA]
Pixie, get over here, right now!

00:09:58.056 --> 00:09:59.349
Yes, at once, sir.

00:09:59.390 --> 00:10:01.392
[TATSUYA]
Honoka, you back up Pixie.

00:10:01.434 --> 00:10:02.644
[HONOKA]
You got it!

00:10:02.685 --> 00:10:04.979
[TATSUYA]
Erika, Leo, stay where you are.

00:10:05.021 --> 00:10:06.981
You can tell that
to the others, too.

00:10:07.023 --> 00:10:08.691
[ERIKA]
Huh...? Okay.

00:10:08.733 --> 00:10:09.943
[LEO]
Uh, right.

00:10:15.824 --> 00:10:18.451
[HONOKA] I agreed to it
without a moment's hesitation,

00:10:18.493 --> 00:10:21.621
but I actually don't know what
"backing up" means in this case.

00:10:23.123 --> 00:10:24.332
[HONOKA gasps]

00:10:27.627 --> 00:10:29.087
[HONOKA] I'm gonna need
to get a good read

00:10:29.129 --> 00:10:31.047
on her situation first.

00:10:48.690 --> 00:10:50.400
[PARASITE D]
We found it.

00:10:50.441 --> 00:10:51.985
[PARASITE E]
We've Found it!

00:10:56.281 --> 00:10:57.532
[PIXIE gasps]

00:11:08.042 --> 00:11:10.879
[PARASITES growl]

00:11:21.472 --> 00:11:22.682
[PIXIE gasps]

00:11:24.309 --> 00:11:26.978
[PARASITES]
Return to us!

00:11:27.020 --> 00:11:30.732
[PIXIE] No, I refuse!
I'm no longer part of you!

00:11:30.773 --> 00:11:33.026
I now belong...

00:11:33.067 --> 00:11:35.486
I belong to "him"!

00:11:35.528 --> 00:11:38.615
[PARASITES] Then your insolence
will be punished!

00:11:42.619 --> 00:11:44.662
What the hell is that?!

00:11:44.704 --> 00:11:47.999
There's a colossal force
bearing down on her.

00:11:48.041 --> 00:11:50.501
Tatsuya, do you
know what it is?

00:11:50.543 --> 00:11:52.420
[MIYUKI] This is the
result of you ignoring

00:11:52.462 --> 00:11:53.713
what Brother told you.

00:11:53.755 --> 00:11:54.839
[ANGIE gasps]

00:11:54.881 --> 00:11:57.383
You killed every parasite
host body in your path

00:11:57.425 --> 00:11:59.093
without a second thought.

00:11:59.135 --> 00:12:02.055
Now they're free and out
on a brutal rampage.

00:12:02.096 --> 00:12:05.892
Lina, how do you plan on making
amends for your carelessness?

00:12:05.934 --> 00:12:08.770
[gasps]
What are you talking about?!

00:12:08.811 --> 00:12:11.356
All I was doing was
carrying out my mission!

00:12:11.397 --> 00:12:13.191
[MIYUKI] Then the least
you could do is clean up

00:12:13.233 --> 00:12:14.984
your own mess.

00:12:15.026 --> 00:12:17.278
Or can you handle that?

00:12:17.320 --> 00:12:19.948
Even Brother is stuck
with having to seal them,

00:12:19.989 --> 00:12:22.909
a far more passive method
than he would prefer.

00:12:22.951 --> 00:12:24.702
I'll make amends! Just watch!

00:12:24.744 --> 00:12:25.578
Lina, wait a minute.

00:12:25.620 --> 00:12:28.248
[ANGIE] Shut up!
I don't want to hear it!

00:12:28.289 --> 00:12:29.832
[LINA] I need to make sure
I pull this mission

00:12:29.874 --> 00:12:31.167
off successfully!

00:12:32.877 --> 00:12:33.962
[LINA]
If I don't...

00:12:34.003 --> 00:12:36.297
...then what am I even
doing in Japan right now?!

00:12:36.339 --> 00:12:38.716
Not to mention
killing my comrades!

00:12:43.179 --> 00:12:44.889
[LINA]
Then a lightning attack...!

00:12:47.141 --> 00:12:49.185
[LINA]
It's not working!

00:12:49.227 --> 00:12:51.437
Maybe air bullets?!

00:12:51.479 --> 00:12:55.024
Ultrasonic waves!
Gravity shock wave!

00:13:03.825 --> 00:13:04.867
[gasps]

00:13:04.909 --> 00:13:06.411
Lina, it's coming!

00:13:08.246 --> 00:13:13.209
[LINA grunts]

00:13:15.086 --> 00:13:15.670
[TATSUYA grunts]

00:13:15.712 --> 00:13:17.255
Brother, be careful!

00:13:21.592 --> 00:13:23.177
[TATSUYA] Miyuki may
have the tactile skill

00:13:23.219 --> 00:13:25.388
to detect spirit
information bodies,

00:13:25.430 --> 00:13:28.141
but not the vision for
a bird's‐eye view.

00:13:28.182 --> 00:13:29.142
Because of that,

00:13:29.183 --> 00:13:31.769
she has difficulty
positioning her attacks.

00:13:33.688 --> 00:13:35.606
[grunts]

00:13:35.648 --> 00:13:39.027
[TATSUYA] It's so taxing to
think about holding out...

00:13:39.068 --> 00:13:41.904
...when you don't even know
how long you'll need to.

00:13:41.946 --> 00:13:46.117
At this rate,
the two might give in.

00:13:46.159 --> 00:13:48.077
Physical attacks wouldn't work.

00:13:48.119 --> 00:13:52.123
If we have any chance, it's
magic that affects the mind.

00:13:52.165 --> 00:13:53.458
Tsk!

00:13:53.499 --> 00:13:55.752
Honestly, it's all we have.

00:13:55.793 --> 00:13:59.130
Mikihiko, do you see what's
happening over here?

00:13:59.172 --> 00:14:01.424
Yeah. I do.

00:14:01.466 --> 00:14:04.260
But I'm in the middle of quickly
making a sealing circle,

00:14:04.302 --> 00:14:06.137
so just hang in there.

00:14:06.179 --> 00:14:07.388
[TATSUYA]
Well, what's the likelihood

00:14:07.430 --> 00:14:10.641
that the sealing circle will
suppress all this, though?

00:14:10.683 --> 00:14:14.395
If I'm being honest,
maybe 50 percent.

00:14:14.437 --> 00:14:18.649
I got it. That's fine.
We only need a moment.

00:14:18.691 --> 00:14:21.235
Try to hold it off
for just ten seconds!

00:14:21.277 --> 00:14:24.197
[ALL gasp]

00:14:26.991 --> 00:14:28.868
[MIKIHIKO]
All right.

00:14:28.910 --> 00:14:30.953
I'll make sure you get
your full ten seconds,

00:14:30.995 --> 00:14:32.163
no matter what it takes.

00:14:32.205 --> 00:14:33.664
I'll help out, too, Tatsuya!

00:14:33.706 --> 00:14:35.041
We got you!

00:14:35.083 --> 00:14:37.460
Good to hear.

00:14:37.502 --> 00:14:39.754
Mikihiko, start the countdown.

00:14:39.796 --> 00:14:41.964
Roger that!

00:14:42.006 --> 00:14:45.802
Three... Two... One...

00:14:45.843 --> 00:14:47.053
Now!

00:14:55.645 --> 00:15:00.691
[PARASITES groan]

00:15:03.611 --> 00:15:05.822
[gasps]

00:15:05.863 --> 00:15:07.073
[HONOKA grunts]

00:15:10.410 --> 00:15:12.537
[MIYUKI]
Huh?

00:15:12.578 --> 00:15:14.956
[gasps]

00:15:14.997 --> 00:15:17.333
Miyuki, look...

00:15:36.978 --> 00:15:40.731
[MIYUKI] This... This is the
world that Brother sees.

00:15:43.401 --> 00:15:46.446
[MIYUKI]
Yes, brother... I see it too!

00:15:51.451 --> 00:15:52.785
There it is.

00:16:00.585 --> 00:16:01.794
[MIYUKI]
Cocytus!

00:16:04.630 --> 00:16:06.799
[PARASITES groan]

00:16:31.073 --> 00:16:35.369
[ALL chuckle happily]

00:16:45.213 --> 00:16:47.006
[MIYUKI exhales]

00:16:47.048 --> 00:16:48.466
[MIYUKI]
Mm?

00:16:48.508 --> 00:16:50.134
[gasps]

00:16:50.176 --> 00:16:51.636
[chuckles]

00:16:57.183 --> 00:16:59.560
Was that just lunar magic?

00:17:01.229 --> 00:17:03.689
[LINA] Even though I
couldn't see the parasite,

00:17:03.731 --> 00:17:07.193
I sensed it was destroyed.

00:17:07.235 --> 00:17:09.737
Lunar magic this powerful...

00:17:11.614 --> 00:17:14.408
[LINA]
Miyuki... Tatsuya...

00:17:14.450 --> 00:17:17.036
What on Earth are
the two of you?!

00:17:22.250 --> 00:17:26.128
Please, Lina, you must never
speak of this to anyone.

00:17:26.170 --> 00:17:28.798
Wha‐‐? Wait, are you serious?

00:17:28.839 --> 00:17:32.552
In exchange, I'll never
reveal your other identity.

00:17:32.593 --> 00:17:35.221
Sirius' secret is safe.

00:17:35.263 --> 00:17:37.848
This applies not only
to Miyuki and me,

00:17:37.890 --> 00:17:41.060
but to everyone else on our end
who's involved in this, too.

00:17:43.479 --> 00:17:46.065
[exhales]
All right, fine.

00:17:46.107 --> 00:17:48.401
If you're really
promising to stay quiet,

00:17:48.442 --> 00:17:51.070
then I won't tell
anyone what I saw here.

00:17:51.112 --> 00:17:54.907
Besides, I bet nobody
would believe me anyway.

00:17:54.949 --> 00:17:57.076
It's a deal.

00:17:57.118 --> 00:17:58.327
[MIYUKI gasps]

00:17:59.453 --> 00:18:02.748
[MIYUKI gasps]

00:18:09.797 --> 00:18:11.048
[TATSUYA]
Lina.

00:18:11.090 --> 00:18:14.051
Huh? Was there something else?

00:18:14.093 --> 00:18:18.097
[TATSUYA] If you ever want
to quit being a soldier,

00:18:18.139 --> 00:18:20.141
I think I can help
you with that.

00:18:22.226 --> 00:18:23.269
Huh?

00:18:23.311 --> 00:18:24.520
[TATSUYA]
I have some acquaintances

00:18:24.562 --> 00:18:26.731
that I can call in favors from.

00:18:26.772 --> 00:18:30.067
[LINA] Hold on, Tatsuya!
Why would you bring that up?!

00:18:30.109 --> 00:18:31.152
You don't get it!

00:18:31.193 --> 00:18:34.530
I don't want to stop being
the Sirius, I like it.

00:18:34.572 --> 00:18:37.116
Ah, I see.

00:18:37.158 --> 00:18:39.785
Sorry, it was a
weird thing to say.

00:18:43.247 --> 00:18:44.457
[gasps]

00:18:50.713 --> 00:18:52.423
[AYAKO]
Your Excellency Kudou,

00:18:52.465 --> 00:18:55.134
I consider it a great
honor to meet you.

00:18:59.555 --> 00:19:03.267
If I may, Sir, my name
is Ayako Kuroba.

00:19:03.309 --> 00:19:05.519
I am of the Yotsuba's
lowest ranks,

00:19:05.561 --> 00:19:07.980
charged with serving our
esteemed family leader,

00:19:08.022 --> 00:19:09.690
Maya Yotsuba.

00:19:09.732 --> 00:19:12.443
A representative
of Lady Yotsuba?

00:19:12.485 --> 00:19:14.278
No wonder you're so levelheaded,

00:19:14.320 --> 00:19:16.572
despite your
obviously young age.

00:19:16.614 --> 00:19:18.449
Alas, Your Excellency,

00:19:18.491 --> 00:19:21.243
we're running regrettably
short on time to chit‐chat,

00:19:21.285 --> 00:19:25.081
so there is one thing I
would like to ask you about.

00:19:25.122 --> 00:19:27.541
By all means, my dear.

00:19:27.583 --> 00:19:29.877
How very kind of you.

00:19:29.919 --> 00:19:31.253
With all due respect,

00:19:31.295 --> 00:19:34.632
I've been led to understand
that Your Excellency's intent

00:19:34.674 --> 00:19:37.802
is to bring back these sealed
monsters called parasites.

00:19:37.843 --> 00:19:41.097
But to be completely honest,
the errand I have been sent on

00:19:41.138 --> 00:19:44.266
by the family head is
to also retrieve them.

00:19:44.308 --> 00:19:46.435
Oh, is it, now?

00:19:47.770 --> 00:19:51.941
Quite fortunately, there are two
sealed vessels here already.

00:19:51.982 --> 00:19:54.360
Why don't each of
us take one of them?

00:19:54.402 --> 00:19:56.987
Does that suit you,
Your Excellency?

00:19:59.699 --> 00:20:01.158
[AYAKO gasps]

00:20:02.660 --> 00:20:06.247
[KUDOU laughs]

00:20:06.288 --> 00:20:07.873
Very well, then.

00:20:07.915 --> 00:20:12.336
We'll try the friendly approach
and share the spoils evenly.

00:20:12.378 --> 00:20:14.130
Thank you, Your Excellency.

00:20:14.171 --> 00:20:16.006
Truly.

00:20:16.048 --> 00:20:17.675
[AYAKO]
Thanks to you, Tatsuya,

00:20:17.717 --> 00:20:20.970
I can finish this mission
without any issues.

00:20:23.806 --> 00:20:26.475
[MIYUKI]
Brother, about Lina...

00:20:26.517 --> 00:20:28.477
Do you think she'll
keep her promise?

00:20:28.519 --> 00:20:31.814
I mean, about what you
asked her not to mention?

00:20:31.856 --> 00:20:34.942
I'm sure Lina has her
own things to deal with.

00:20:34.984 --> 00:20:38.154
We all struggle to get places
we want to go sometimes.

00:20:38.195 --> 00:20:41.198
Seems her battle to do so
is no different than mine.

00:20:41.240 --> 00:20:43.159
But despite her stubbornness,

00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:46.412
you still made an offer
to help her anyway.

00:20:46.454 --> 00:20:47.955
Why'd you do that?

00:20:47.997 --> 00:20:49.540
I'm not sure I understand.

00:20:49.582 --> 00:20:51.167
What I mean, Brother,

00:20:51.208 --> 00:20:54.503
is why do you keep on
trying to help Lina?

00:20:54.545 --> 00:20:56.005
Could it be that...

00:20:56.046 --> 00:20:59.133
...you might be harboring
some special feelings for her?

00:20:59.175 --> 00:21:00.259
[gasps]

00:21:00.301 --> 00:21:04.013
I just thought leaving the Stars
might carve a better future.

00:21:04.054 --> 00:21:07.433
It's not as simple as just
leaving the military, either.

00:21:07.475 --> 00:21:10.019
I truly think the
best option for Lina,

00:21:10.060 --> 00:21:13.564
is if she becomes
naturalized here in Japan.

00:21:13.606 --> 00:21:16.525
But I do still
sympathize with her.

00:21:16.567 --> 00:21:20.613
In more ways than one,
we're actually very much alike.

00:21:20.654 --> 00:21:22.531
Or, maybe I should say

00:21:22.573 --> 00:21:25.951
we fall in to the same
category of people.

00:21:25.993 --> 00:21:29.663
Neither one of us had
any real choice or say

00:21:29.705 --> 00:21:32.917
in the path that took
us where we are now.

00:21:32.958 --> 00:21:34.794
You could call me
enrolling at First High

00:21:34.835 --> 00:21:37.213
a decision I forced
them to let me have,

00:21:37.254 --> 00:21:41.217
but honestly, I don't think
Lina was even allowed that much.

00:21:43.052 --> 00:21:45.012
[TATSUYA]
I was never given a choice,

00:21:45.054 --> 00:21:49.099
but one day, I'll create my own,
and choose for myself.

00:21:49.141 --> 00:21:51.811
I figured I'd offer
help out of friendship.

00:21:51.852 --> 00:21:52.937
That is, of course,

00:21:52.978 --> 00:21:55.356
assuming Lina wanted the
same thing out of the deal,

00:21:55.397 --> 00:22:00.569
but... I suppose it was
none of my business.

00:22:00.611 --> 00:22:01.821
[MIYUKI]
Huh?

00:22:06.200 --> 00:22:08.035
[TATSUYA gasps]

00:22:08.077 --> 00:22:11.372
No, Brother, that isn't
true at all.

00:22:11.413 --> 00:22:15.668
I'd bet you almost anything
that some far off day...

00:22:18.671 --> 00:22:21.465
...or even...
in the near future,

00:22:21.507 --> 00:22:25.094
your kindness will
ultimately reach her heart.

00:22:25.135 --> 00:22:28.222
Because I have a feeling
that this incident tonight

00:22:28.264 --> 00:22:30.558
surely must have made
Lina see her current self

00:22:30.599 --> 00:22:32.393
and what could change.

00:22:32.434 --> 00:22:34.603
She may seem
a little bit simple,

00:22:34.645 --> 00:22:37.565
but she can definitely
be sharp, too.

00:22:37.606 --> 00:22:38.816
[gasps]

00:22:42.444 --> 00:22:44.572
Miyuki...

00:22:44.613 --> 00:22:47.116
[TATSUYA]
Simple? That's kind of mean.

00:22:48.784 --> 00:22:50.619
[BOTH giggle]

00:22:50.661 --> 00:22:55.666
♪

